# Event Message Reliability

- Consumers must be idempotent.
- Use retry with bounded backoff and dead-letter handling.
- Persist processing checkpoints/offset intent safely.
- Include message keys for ordering-sensitive streams.

## Minimum checklist

- [ ] Duplicate detection strategy documented
- [ ] Poison message path defined
- [ ] Observability metrics for consumer lag and failures
